当我们谈论对象的形状(shape of an object)时，我们指的是属性的名称及其值的类型.

6.3 Wider vs. Narrower

ANYTHING: any
ARRAY: any[]
ARRAY OF STRING: string[]
ARRAY OF 3: [string,string,string]
